reviews.review_text: Jerry Chain Smoking I remember Jerry chain smoking through Space when I was looking at him through binoculars. He must of hot-boxed 3 smokes. The Candyman Jam is classic and Brent boasts some great BGD vocals. This show reminds you why Jerry missed Brent the most after his smack OD. -

Like it was yesterday What a great show.  Was in the orchestra pit with Tom Stack of Grateful Dead Productions.  Remember the Don't Ease Me In...we could not stop singing that tune at end of set.  After show got lost on campus and ended up driving our car in pedestrian only places.  Was with dear departed friend Ali.  Will never forget the good times.
